highlights.text: Bad Bunny has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “DtMF” is the highest at #3.
“Die With A Smile” by Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 148 days straight.
“Are You Even Real (feat. Givēon)” by Teddy Swims and GIVĒON is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #30.
“Eusexua” by FKA twigs is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 25 spots at #43.
